  (9902783, '(Completed Job) Ciampa, Melissa', 'Melissa Ciampa', '13403 Margate Street', 'Sherman Oaks', 'CA', '91401', '(.PM) Jorge Flores,Nicole Antoine', 'This client was one of the first clients i met when myself and Brian went on my training.  It took them this long to make a decision so I would be weary of giving them too many options.  We have to be in total control on this project because they ask a LOT of questions. They are super nice so as long as we Project Manage them it should be a great project! More to do in Phase 2 in the backyard with pool decking and pool coping, tile, etc.

