  (7484154, '(Completed Job) Garcia, Kat', 'Kat Garcia', '15444 Mustang Ln', 'North Hills', 'CA', '91343', '(.PM) Jorge Flores', 'Very nice and reasonable client. Client will more than likely be working from home during this projected start date.
